::Slayer::

Slayer growls as 13 of the shots hit his armor, making further dents 
in it. He speeds up, flying toward the Iron Fist and toward Wheeljack.

He fires several missiles at Wheeljack, but they are intercepted by 
the shields and neutralized. Slayer swears, climbing back up and 
avoiding a missile from the Iron Fist.
